#WIll's dir
#obs_dir = '/glade/p/cgd/tss/people/wwieder/inputdata/single_point/datmdata_RC/US-Rls/'
#Derek main dir
obs_dir = '/glade/u/home/dpierson/clm50bgc_US-Rls_test/obs/'

obs_years = range(2016,2018)
obs_nmon = 12
obs_monthly_filenames = [obs_dir + str(obs_years[i])+'-'+str(m+1).zfill(2)+'.nc' for i 
                         in range(len(obs_years)) for m in range(obs_nmon)]  

print(obs_monthly_filenames)

# print for clarity
print('----- Monthly obs filenames -----')
print(obs_monthly_filenames[1])
print(obs_monthly_filenames[2])
print('etc.....')
print()

# join monthly obs data into on variable
rawOBS = utils.time_set_mid(xr.open_mfdataset(obs_monthly_filenames, 
                                             decode_times=True, 
                                             combine='by_coords'), 
                           'time')
# index the filed obs array by location
OBS = rawOBS.isel(lat=0, lon=0)

# print for clarity
print('----- Field Obs Array Info -----')
print(OBS)
print()

# convert obs GPP units from umol/m2/s to g/m2/h
OBS['GPP'] = OBS.GPP * 1e-6 * 12.01 * 3600
OBS['GPP'].attrs['units'] = 'gC/m2/h'

# get simulation data
case = 'clm50bgc_US-Rls_test'
sim_years = range(2016,2018)
CLMdir = '/glade/u/home/dpierson/' + case +'/lnd/hist/' 
CLMfile = [CLMdir + case + '.clm2.h1.' + str(sim_years[i]) +'-01-01-00000.nc' for i in range(len(sim_years))]  

SIM  = xr.open_mfdataset(CLMfile, decode_times=True, combine='by_coords')
SIM  = SIM.isel(lndgrid=0)

# shift CLM time to match OBS
SIM = SIM.shift(time=-1)
print(SIM)

Plot soil temperature¶

In [15]:
simTSOId = SIM.TSOI.resample(time="24H").mean().sel(levgrnd = 0.1, method='nearest')
simTSOId = simTSOId - 273.15 #convert from K to C

plt.figure(figsize=[15,4])
plt.plot(simTSOId) 
plt.title('CLM Soil Temperature @ ~10 cm', loc='left', fontsize='medium', fontweight='bold');
plt.ylabel('TSOI @ ~10 cm (deg C)');
